## ğŸš€ Quickstart

```bash
# Setup environment
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .
cp .env.example .env  # add your OPENAI_API_KEY

# Boot the system
python -m echo_os.cli boot

# Plan a project
